Rating: 4
Wonderful and easy. I used bread from a loaf of rosemary bread I'd baked a few days earlier. The recipe was super easy and delicious. Like others, I found it under done at the end of the specified cooking time, so I turned the heat up to 400, cooked it about 5-10 more minutes, then put the oven on broil for the last couple of minutes to get the tops golden. A complete success!

